<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .success-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #2eb67d;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .next-steps {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="success-icon">âœ…</div>
        <h1><%= message %></h1>
        <p>Your Slack bot has been successfully installed and is ready to use. You can now start interacting with the bot in your Slack workspace.</p>
        
        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Try sending a message to your bot</li>
                <li>Configure bot settings if needed</li>
                <li>Check the documentation for advanced features</li>
                <li>Restart your Slack client if you don't see the bot</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>